[OVERLAY] VimFu — Recipe: Clean Trailing Whitespace
[SAY] This file has invisible trailing spaces on most lines. Let's reveal them and clean them up.
[SAY] First make whitespace visible.
[TYPE] ':set list listchars=tab:>-,trail:·,space:·'

